did-joe-biden-use-the-hammer-to-steal-the-election%2F&d=TOASGvm2FfjCvYiV2fDq71NDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=3b3b2ede\" target=\"_blank\">https://newswithviews.com/did-joe-biden-use-the-hammer-to-steal-the-election/</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T12:11:43.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">super-surveillance system THE HAMMER </code></pre>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T12:14:40.000Z","msg":"yes<br />\n雖然唔知乜野黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T12:20:31.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">In August 2015, a CIA contractor-turned-whistleblower, Dennis L. Montgomery provided the FBI and the Department of Justice a large amount of surveillance data in 47 hard drives.\n\nThese hard drives involved the evidence of activities of Robert Hunter Biden, the son of the former U.S. Vice President Joe Biden and Joe Biden himself.\n\nAccording to Montgomery, there are 600 million pages of files stored on 47 hard drives which were handed over to the FBI.\n\nAmong these hard drives, there are 10,000 pages of documents, videos and images in relation to Hunter Biden, and his father Joe Biden, the former U.S. Vice President to President Obama.\n\nSince 2003, Montgomery believes that the United States government has surveillanced Joe Biden and Hunter Biden through a super-surveillance system called 「The HAMMER.」</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">The tapes also reveal that the Foreign Intelligence Surveillance court (FISA), Supreme Court Chief Justice John Roberts, 156 other judges, members of Congress, and Donald J. Trump were targeted by THE HAMMER.</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">The 47 Hard Drives and The Hammer super-surveillance system</span><br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/@fan.matisse/the-47-hard-drives-and-the-hammer-super-surveillance-system-1b6e0d6deb3a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40fan.matisse%2Fthe-47-hard-drives-and-the-hammer-super-surveillance-sy